I"g<p>When doing data analysis in R, we often want to sort a vector or <a href="https://masterr.org/r/how-to-easily-sort-a-data-frame/">data frame</a>. Sometimes, we want to undo the sorting. This usually happens inside of a function where you want to first sort the input object, do some operations and undo the sorting before you return the output object.</p>
